		<img src="/css/img/add_comment.png" alt="Add Comment"> <a href="/posts/should-i-refactor-this-piece-of-code:480f4dd6-eafc-4fd3-9302-4f44cbdd56cb#CommentAddForm">Add Comment</a>	</div>
